      "date": "2013-01-10 12:35:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/0f8ee33e-5b1a-11e2-8985-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
