        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-01-10 18:30:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n== sanity test 56w: check lfs_migrate -c stripe_count works == 18:28:50 (1357784930)\n/usr/bin/lfs_migrate -y -c 6 /mnt/lustre/d0.sanity/d56w/file1\n/usr/bin/lfs_migrate: line 100: /bin: is a directory\n sanity test_56w: @@@@@@ FAIL: /usr/bin/lfs_migrate -y -c 6 /mnt/lustre/d0.sanity/d56w/file1 failed \n\nThe error is right in the code path we just changed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
